snippet.title: Gladihoppers (Trailer #2 iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
Gladihoppers is a unique 2d physics based mobile gladiator game. Now with a Career mode!

Available for free on:
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gladihoppers/id1447035711?mt=8
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DreamonStudios.Gladihoppers
Itch: https://dreamonstudios.itch.io/gladihoppers
